# Summary
Cordial integration with Amplitude enables bidirectional data flow: sending Amplitude cohorts to Cordial lists for targeted messaging, and streaming real-time customer behavior and profile data from Cordial to Amplitude for enhanced analysis across email, SMS, and mobile app touchpoints.

